1
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:15,240
Brother Sun, can I...

2
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,280
Stop right there.

3
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:17,740
Want an extension?

4
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,600
Don't even ask.

5
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,840
If everyone were like you,

6
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,680
my boys and I would starve.

7
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:23,760
No.

8
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:25,120
I wanted to ask,

9
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:29,600
if I can pay it all off at once.

10
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,680
Count it.

11
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,800
Where did you strike it rich?

12
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,240
You sound so confident.

13
00:01:40,160 --> 00:01:41,960
It's all there.

14
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:47,440
Qiang, where did you get this windfall?

15
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:49,479
You want to know?

16
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:50,120
Come here.

17
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,320
It's none of your business.

18
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:54,880
Brother, it's all here.

19
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:58,960
Boss Sun, as for us,

20
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:00,920
we part ways here.

21
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,520
Let's never meet again.

22
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:13,000
Mom, did you have your chemo today?

23
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,880
No.

24
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,000
The doctor said...

25
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,040
I'll go pay.

26
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:16,960
Don't.

27
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:19,410
I want to be discharged.

28
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,120
How can you be discharged?

29
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:23,720
You'll be fine after a few more months of chemo.

30
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,440
It costs too much.

31
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,720
Mom, I told you.

32
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,320
Don't worry about the money.

33
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,680
Just relax, okay?

34
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,960
I'll go pay.

35
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,880
Just stay put, okay?

36
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,840
That should be enough.

37
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:45,680
Yes.

38
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,160
It's enough.

39
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,880
With the previous arrears

40
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:51,560
and this week's fees, 12,000 is just enough.

41
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,890
Remember to pay on time.

42
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,240
Okay.

43
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,160
Here. Count it.

44
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,600
Don't fall behind on payments again.

45
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,400
Thanks.

46
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,560
I won't fall behind again.

47
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,400
Okay.

48
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,040
Xiaoyuan.

49
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,200
It's pretty hot today.

50
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,850
Let's head back to the ward.

51
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:08,800
Gang, come sit.

52
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,290
How are you feeling?

53
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,760
Much better.

54
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:16,519
Don't worry.

55
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,120
I promise you'll get better.

56
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,290
It's okay, Gang.

57
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:25,440
This is the Dayang Village disease.

58
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,920
It's also our fate.

59
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:32,760
All the kids in Dayang Village get this.

60
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:37,000
So, Gang, I'm fine.

61
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,690
This isn't Dayang Village's fate.

62
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:47,000
And it's not Dayang Village's disease.

63
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,420
Do you understand?

64
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:56,200
Xiaoyuan, let's go back.

65
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:58,440
Okay.

66
00:04:58,440 --> 00:05:00,720
Yang Gang, we're leaving.

67
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:03,680
Take care.

68
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,720
Gang, I'm heading out.

69
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,600
Gang.

70
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,240
Xiaofeng? What are you doing here?

71
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,040
Have a seat.

72
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:29,580
Liao Fei asked me to bring you this fruit.

73
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:32,880
Last time, he acted on impulse because of Fan.

74
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:35,400
Sorry about that.

75
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,920
I didn't take it to heart.

76
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:39,240
I understand Liao Fei.

77
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,440
By the way, I wanted to ask you something.

78
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:44,500
Didn't you use to be a good student when you were little?

79
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:47,360
Back then, I remember your mom taking your report card...

80
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,000
...and showing it off everywhere.

81
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,200
She'd tell everyone in the villages,

82
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,320
"Look how good my child's grades are."

83
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,400
So why did you...

84
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,280
...start hanging out with Liao Fei...

85
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:55,880
...and stop going to school?

86
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,300
I didn't want this either.

87
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,100
We ran out of money.

88
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,780
Couldn't afford school anymore.

89
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:06,240
Doesn't Dayang Village...

90
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:09,000
...have that national financial aid?

91
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,060
Where is the money?

92
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,900
With Xiao Tianman around,

93
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,580
how would that money ever reach our pockets?

94
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,490
Xiao Tianman...

95
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,360
Xiaofeng, listen.

96
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:24,120
Don't hang out with Liao Fei anymore.

97
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:26,360
You need to go back to school.

98
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:28,440
As for the tuition fees,

99
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,250
you don't need to worry.

100
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:33,440
I'll find a way to pay for it.

101
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,760
Just stop hanging around Liao Fei.

102
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:37,520
There's no future in that.

103
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,940
Can I really go back to school?

104
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,000
Really.

105
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:47,520
Have an apple.

106
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:49,450
I just bought them. They're sweet.

107
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,600
Look at the time.

108
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,960
Why isn't Gang out yet?

109
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,170
Where's Godmother?

110
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,540
Yeah, where is she?

111
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,130
I'm not leaving.

112
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,920
I want to stay.

113
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:32,690
Didn't we agree to leave together?

114
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,730
What do you mean?

115
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,560
I want to mine some more gold.

116
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,240
You want to go back to the gold mine?

117
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,570
Do you have a death wish?

118
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,490
I finally found a rich mine.

119
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,720
I want to make more money.

120
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:47,000
I'll meet you in the city afterwards. Okay?

121
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:49,450
Brother, you really can't go back.

122
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,000
We finally saved enough money.

123
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,520
It's enough for Godmother's treatment, isn't it?

124
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,920
Brother, how about this?

125
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:57,760
Come south with us. It's easy to make money there.

126
00:07:57,760 --> 00:08:00,800
Right. Let's go to the city and live a stable life.

127
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,040
A stable life?

128
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:06,440
How can we be stable with that little money?

129
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:10,760
Make money fast? What's faster than mining gold?

130
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:15,360
I found that mine myself.

131
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,060
Why should I let Xiao Tianman have it?

132
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,080
Xiao Tianman can make money.

133
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,210
Situ can make money.

134
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,610
Gaoshan can make money.

135
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,560
Why can't I?

136
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:26,820
They all come from poor families.

137
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,320
I can be a big boss too.

138
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,680
Brother, are you crazy?

139
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,210
You're the one who's crazy.

140
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,000
Let me tell you something.

141
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,360
It's decided.

142
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:39,120
You two go to the city and wait for me.

143
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,200
Also,

144
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,820
when the three of us are together,

145
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,680
sometimes you two hold me back.

146
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,880
To put it bluntly,

147
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,800
you two are a burden to me.

148
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,860
Because you're too unprofessional.

149
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,840
You go ahead.

150
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,120
Bro.

151
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,320
Bro.

152
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:03,200
Is he crazy about money?

153
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,680
He must be out of his mind.

154
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:14,100
He's definitely keeping something from us.

155
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:36,960
Come in.

156
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:42,600
Du Jing, you're back.

157
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:44,760
I'm back. Just a moment.

158
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,320
Well?

159
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,080
Any news?

160
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,160
I've asked everyone.

161
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,680
No one in Jiang Xiaomei's hometown has seen her parents.

162
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:58,010
Otherwise, I would have heard something.

163
00:09:58,880 --> 00:09:59,920
I figured.

164
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:03,280
I had someone check the ticket records at the train station.

165
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:05,010
She really didn't buy a ticket.

166
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,500
I suspect Xiao Tianman has her locked up.

167
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,720
So what do we do now?

168
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,360
I've already informed the police.

169
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,960
They are investigating now.

170
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:16,690
Hopefully, there will be a good outcome soon.

171
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,000
I hope so.

172
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,000
Come in.

173
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,560
Miss Situ.

174
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,880
Du Jing is back, too.

175
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,640
Why?

176
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,410
Didn't you want me back?

177
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,680
Not at all.

178
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,480
Here's the thing.

179
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,200
Director Xiao...

180
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:39,280
cordially invites you to dinner tomorrow night.

181
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:41,960
He hopes you can make it.

182
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,480
Du Jing, you should come too.

183
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,480
All right.

184
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:52,160
Tell Boss Xiao,

185
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:54,600
Du Jing and I will be there on time.

186
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:58,120
Good. I'll take my leave then.

187
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,520
I won't keep you.
